A4.text: It is best known as the venue for the Wimbledon Championships.

A5.text: The All England Lawn Tennis and Croquet Club is a private members' club based at Church Road in the Wimbledon area of London, England.

A6.text: Club page on the Wimbledon Championships site

A7.text: The Wimbledon Championships, commonly called Wimbledon, is a tennis tournament organised by the All England Lawn Tennis and Croquet Club.
